AniSOAP Optimization Study
Copyright 2025 Tejas Dahiya

This repository preserves a profiling and optimization study of AniSOAP
conducted during a Fall 2025 Open Source Program Office internship with the
Cersonsky Lab at the University of Wisconsin-Madison.

AniSOAP is developed by the Cersonsky Lab and distributed under the Apache
License, Version 2.0:
https://github.com/cersonsky-lab/AniSOAP

AniSOAP is an external project and is not redistributed as part of this
repository. The DOI-backed v0.0.0 study is preserved at:
https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17519888

The maintained successor implementation is AniSOAP-Torch:
https://github.com/Tejas7007/AniSOAP-Torch
